overview: While young Jaromir is recovering from eye surgery, he lies on the bed feeling vulnerable. When Dr. Vostry sees how his patient feels, he decides he must attend to all of Jaromir's needs with some extra special personal attention. With this sort of special daily attention, Jaromir's remaining stay in the hospital shouldn't be too bad at all!  William Higgins continues his popular medical fantasy series where innocent young men receive more than they expected when visiting the randy doctor and his assistant male nurse. These "professionals" really like to check out the handsome young guys. These guys are just following orders when the doctor says, "Open wide!"
title: Czech Up 5
